It doesn't matter if any one of your predictions come true or not, all I know is that for the first few months the game will be pure. Every game I've played from the beginning of when it comes out has been fantastic. No one knows anything, everyone is a newborn infant. We are all on the same playing field. <P>Only later does it get bad. That's when people start "experimenting," stripping the game down to it's most basic concepts. Then they start telling others of their findings. It becomes a science. Then, and only then, will we get the Naked Casters, the Uber Templates. Of course, we'll only get naked casters if someone decides after doing research that proves it's more efficient to be naked.<P>--------------------<P>Cavernshark<BR>-------------------------<BR>(Name and Such Undecided)
